        <Parent_String>marks by function [300028756], marks (identifying markings) [300028744], identifying markings and symbols [300157238], documents by function [300137955], document genres [300026031], information forms (objects) [300220751], Information Forms (hierarchy name) [300026029], Visual and Verbal Communication (hierarchy name) [300264552], Objects Facet [300264092]</Parent_String>
